# deepCommodity — cron schedule (UTC). 24/7 crypto + equities (US hours).
# Install on the remote with `crontab -e` and paste the entries below
# (adjust REPO if your checkout lives elsewhere).
# Crypto executes here on the VPS because Binance geo-blocks the Anthropic cloud
# egress (HTTP 451) — the VPS must be in a Binance-allowed region.
# All routines log to $REPO/logs/<routine>.log; failures ping Telegram via run_routine.sh.

REPO=/srv/deepCommodity
SHELL=/bin/bash

# Decision — every 4h, 24/7. Crypto always; US equities when markets are open.
0 */4 * * *        $REPO/deploy/run_routine.sh decision

# Position management — 4x/day, offset 3h from decision. Drawdown breaker + close/trail; never opens.
0 3,9,15,21 * * *  $REPO/deploy/run_routine.sh position-mgmt

# Weekly review — Sunday 18:00 UTC.
0 18 * * 0         $REPO/deploy/run_routine.sh weekly-review

# (Optional) Heartbeat liveness canary — uncomment if you want an independent alive-check.
# 3 * * * *        $REPO/deploy/run_routine.sh heartbeat
